data.description: Charming two story situated on a large corner lot complete with lovely living room with carpeting, built-in bookcases, large windows, and fireplace with tile surround, formal and informal dining areas, light and bright kitchen with hardwood floors, built-in desk, pantry area, lazy susan, and breakfast bar.  Main floor laundry room with closet space, cabinet space, and hanging rod.  Spend peaceful nights in the spacious master suite complete with carpeting, neural decor, large windows, trayed ceiling with ceiling fan, his and her walk-in closets, and private bathroom with his and her sink, oversized corner jetted tub, and tile shower with dual shower heads.  The second level also features three additional bedrooms and a full bathroom.  The finished basement includes another spacious bedroom with viewout window, a full bathroom, and family room with fireplace, tile flooring, neutral decor, and sliding glass door to the patio.  Sit back and relax out on the newer composite deck that is partially covered overlooking the fenced backyard, patio area, and shed!  This home also features newer Impact Resistant roofing, all new double hung vinyl windows, new carpeting, fresh paint, and sprinkler system with irrigation well.
